---
title: Sticky Tofu Pilaf with Mango Chutney
description: Going meat-free has never been easier with recipes like our sticky tofu and fragrant pilaf rice! Mango chutney lends a delicious sweet and tangy taste that’s perfect with satisfyingly crispy tofu. Throw in some fresh veggies and it seems we’ve got a winner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sticky-tofu-pilaf-87e67bb2-28e1bc15.jpg
